 145 |     previous candidate.
 146 | 
 147 |     When reading iteration stats, distinguish the fields carefully:
 148 |     - `global.global_best_score` is the best score found up to and including
 149 |       that iteration.
 150 |     - `global.current_iteration_best_score` is the best score among programs
 151 |       produced in that specific iteration.
 152 |     - `iteration_result.child_program.metrics.combined_score` is the score of
 153 |       the newly generated child for that iteration.
 154 |     - A plateau means the child scores are failing to exceed the running best
 155 |       for several iterations, even if `global_best_score` remains high.
